item.title: About
item.description: Hey, here is something about me: My name is Sudhanshu Choudhary. I am 13 years old. I am a young programmer. Experienced with programming languages as Python and C++. Student at Kendriya Vidyalaya. 8th grader. Developer of the action called Doctor Colors Questions on the Google Assistant app. Have won prizes like a Google T-Shirt and a Google Home.
